% Instructions

- Use context managers (with sqlite3.connect) for all database operations
- Include module docstring explaining cache location, environment variables, and key features
- Singleton pattern: guard _cache_instance to prevent multiple instances
- Cleanup strategy: expire stale entries before enforcing limits via access-time ordering
- Use atomic upsert (INSERT ON CONFLICT) for cache set operations
